    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.poster.avif?t=1688222959\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.webm?t=1688222959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/6ffe13c922a22981f7063b07f69f9ae1.mp4?t=1688222959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Saomi</strong> 是一个喜欢挑战和探索新地方的小冒险家。 在这次冒险中，Saomi 开始寻找一颗非常稀有的钻石，该钻石丢失在一个古老的家族宝藏中。<br>在冒险过程中，Saomi 会奔跑、跳过障碍物、使用二段跳来跳过更大的障碍物、使用她的空中推力技能来躲避陷阱、沿着墙壁跳跃和滑行等等，以寻找丢失的宝藏。<br>快来帮助 Saomi 完成这个伟大而奇妙的冒险吧！<br><br><strong>技能：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>跑<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/c0a833865fc6db3ec6f6d6be0f337db7.poster.avif?t=1688222959\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/c0a833865fc6db3ec6f6d6be0f337db7.webm?t=1688222959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/c0a833865fc6db3ec6f6d6be0f337db7.mp4?t=1688222959\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>跳<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/02c44be0513696e9e2e5a4734887ef14.poster.avif?t=1688222959\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885670/extras/02c44be0513696e9e2e5a4734887ef14.webm?t=1688222959\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared